WEBVTT

00:00.726 --> 00:02.828
Previously on <i>Falling Skies...</i>

00:03.216 --> 00:05.068
Skitters hit us,
and they hit us hard.

00:05.093 --> 00:06.608
They're coming
this way next.

00:06.633 --> 00:09.255
You're supposed to send
anyone under 20 ahead with me.

00:09.311 --> 00:10.895
I don't think anybody's
gonna go for this.

00:10.920 --> 00:12.120
102.

00:12.921 --> 00:14.814
You just did
102 push-ups!

00:14.839 --> 00:16.821
He's like...
A different kid.

00:16.846 --> 00:18.971
If our patrols tell us
an attack is imminent,

00:18.996 --> 00:20.585
a head start
could save lives.

00:20.610 --> 00:21.921
Skitter!

00:24.864 --> 00:26.260
I've decided
to send Matt and Ben

00:26.285 --> 00:27.295
along with
Lieutenant Clayton.

00:27.320 --> 00:28.736
Our kids are our future,

00:28.761 --> 00:30.751
and their safety
has got to come first.

00:32.322 --> 00:34.145
I can take you
to your family, Eli.

00:34.170 --> 00:35.370
[ Groaning ]

00:36.372 --> 00:37.770
And you'll bring more
in two days?

00:37.795 --> 00:38.995
That's the deal.

00:40.948 --> 00:43.509
I knew it was a good idea
to keep you alive, Pope.

00:47.631 --> 00:49.166
[ Panting ]

00:52.036 --> 00:55.171
[ Indistinct shouting
and light applause ]

01:00.743 --> 01:02.510
Oh, sorry!

01:02.545 --> 01:04.245
[ Cheering ]

01:04.279 --> 01:06.180
Yeah, I'll get it
back out to you.

01:06.215 --> 01:10.019
Young man: Take it, Jimmy.
Take it! Take it! Take it!

01:10.054 --> 01:13.223
Jimmy, I'm open! Over here! Jimmy,
I'm open! I'm open! Come on!

01:13.258 --> 01:15.560
Over here!

01:15.594 --> 01:16.662
[ Indistinct shouting ]

01:21.237 --> 01:23.673
[ Shouting ]

01:23.708 --> 01:25.409
Ah. Lourdes.

01:25.443 --> 01:27.746
Oh, come on, guys.
We can take them. We can take them.

01:27.781 --> 01:29.615
Boy:
You weren't even trying!

01:29.650 --> 01:31.751
<i>I</i> wasn't trying?
You just showed up!

01:31.786 --> 01:34.288
Yeah, what were <i>you</i>
<i>doing over there?</i>

01:34.323 --> 01:35.590
Tessa: Just leaving me
all by myself.

01:35.624 --> 01:36.891
Hal: Come on, guys!
Keep your heads up!

01:36.926 --> 01:38.026
We can take them!
Let's do this!

01:38.060 --> 01:40.029
Sanctuary 8,
2nd Mass. Zero?

01:40.064 --> 01:42.231
- I don't think so.
- [ Chuckling ] Oh.

01:42.266 --> 01:44.133
Well, you may have us
on age and height,

01:44.168 --> 01:45.802
and there's something
you need to know

01:45.837 --> 01:47.004
about the 2nd Mass.,
Tessa.

01:47.038 --> 01:48.006
Mm.
We don't give up.

01:48.040 --> 01:49.308
[ Chuckles ]

01:49.342 --> 01:50.375
I'll walk it out.

01:53.514 --> 01:56.116
- Didn't you see me there?
- I was right there.

01:56.151 --> 01:57.452
Yeah, yeah.
I saw you.

01:57.486 --> 01:59.253
Just stay away
from me, okay?

01:59.288 --> 02:00.488
Hey, they're going back.

02:00.523 --> 02:02.190
Yeah, Clayton's walking
our fighter escorts

02:02.224 --> 02:03.591
to the main road.

02:03.626 --> 02:06.528
If the Skitter attack's as bad
as they say it's gonna be,

02:06.562 --> 02:08.463
they'll be happy
to have them back.

02:08.497 --> 02:10.232
When's dad
gonna catch up?

02:10.265 --> 02:12.935
Soon as the 3rd Mass.
makes the rendezvous --

02:12.969 --> 02:14.102
couple days Max.

02:17.206 --> 02:19.941
Hey. I miss him, too.

02:22.345 --> 02:24.779
All right, guys.

02:29.552 --> 02:30.552
[ Indistinct shouting ]

02:30.586 --> 02:31.586
Tessa!

02:34.224 --> 02:35.858
Hal: Take it, Jimmy!
Take it! Take it!

02:35.893 --> 02:37.594
You're not gonna let them
score even once?

02:37.628 --> 02:38.762
You know <i>me.</i>

02:38.796 --> 02:41.598
Yeah. That's right.
I do.

02:43.536 --> 02:45.036
You like <i>that</i> one,
don't you?

02:45.070 --> 02:46.938
Dad.

02:46.972 --> 02:49.708
You know why
they're here.

02:49.742 --> 02:51.276
Just...

02:53.246 --> 02:54.980
...Don't like him
too much.

02:59.696 --> 03:03.696
